{"tid":2287701,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈突然自曝已舉辦了婚禮：這是一場不得已的聯姻","createTime":"2020-11-16T03:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T09:06:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c41c52a39b28da2006fea7e55e96b23dee8e9e","tid":2287701,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"Super Junior金希澈突然自爆結婚了，還感謝前去參加他婚禮的賓客們。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n15日，金希澈在個人IG上寫道：「再次感謝今天忙中抽空來參加我婚禮的所有賓客們。」什麼？歐巴就這樣靜悄悄結婚了，粉絲們怎麼一點消息都沒得到？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這一切因金希澈貼出的遊戲截圖解開了謎底，原來是遊戲中的婚禮啊。金希澈還說：「大家看我的表情就知道，這是一場為了提升攻擊力的聯姻，我實在沒辦法不結...婚禮結束了，我的心情也就這樣，心裡滿是空虛，連婚禮場地都是我定的，9999圓婚訊報道也是我給的錢！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4b56baace797a7707fd4ee535bbba77e/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131672-884982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4b56baace797a7707fd4ee535bbba77e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131672-884982.jpg&h=5d0e5e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞笑的是金希澈還在文字後面連發了數個話題標籤#東方不敗#攻擊力提升之後立刻就離婚#我結婚的話我媽就要退出《我家的熊孩子》了，嗚嗚嗚等，順便還提到了出演《我家的熊孩子》的媽媽金順子女士。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f7fcba2d148fbbdde9ffbc411246d97a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131672-884983.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f7fcba2d148fbbdde9ffbc411246d97a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131672-884983.jpg&h=331adc4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_050637e34142bf4d13905f6252bee2dc/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131672-884984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_050637e34142bf4d13905f6252bee2dc%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131672-884984.jpg&h=a7d68554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9c1f334621e2bbed0e73f8a93db0540c/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131672-884985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9c1f334621e2bbed0e73f8a93db0540c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131672-884985.jpg&h=644f946f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐巴已經到了結婚的年紀，結婚無可厚非，但粉絲們真心希望婚禮不要瞞著大家，不要像這次一樣婚禮結束之後才通知，真的讓大家嚇一跳。得知原來是一場遊戲裡的虛擬婚姻後，粉絲們也大方地送上祝福，表示：「哥哥，新婚快樂」、「歐巴，你想要笑死我啊」、「哈哈哈哈，你瘋了」等。<br />\n<br />\n「圖：金希澈IG」"},{"pid":"114e52e55675808445433d28f9af2dff8b7d42d2","tid":2287701,"uid":256952,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1803132d9191c8fd21ee69e90a69e662cc1ed746","tid":2287701,"uid":320204,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"金希澈我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1fb94b2274163d7ab036dc501275bf1aa54a8d","tid":2287701,"uid":173060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"乜鳩game 黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9850c96fd018ac0cd447ea3f63630fc9b5aacc","tid":2287701,"uid":223912,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s